## How to use

Add the following `v-rapper-mcp` to your configuration:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "v-rapper-mcp": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "v-rapper-mcp"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

And then, just enjoy it!!!

